tment Council, Hajiya Asabe Mnasur Ahmed. Over 300 key investment and trade participants from across the globe are attending the event. Jibrin Ndace  Suleiman idris is a graduate of Fed Univ of Tech Minna (BTECH Mathematics/Comp Science), Specialist in ICT Support Services. also proficient in use of online journalism tools & Social media management. I currently serve as I.T Officer with Africa's Largest TV Network NTA